teetime.framework.pipe

Interface IPipe<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the elements which this pipe should transfer.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPipe, AbstractSynchedPipe, AbstractUnsynchedPipe, BoundedSynchedPipe, DummyPipe, InstantiationPipe, ReflexivePipe, UnboundedSynchedPipe, UnsynchedPipe

    public interface IPipe<T>
    Represents a pipe that connects an output port with an input port.
    Author:
    Christian Wulf (chw)
